              "id": "#ask-act-kind-required-on-every-notification",
              "type": "SparqlAskAssertion",
              "query": "ASK { <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/shacl/ProjectionNotificationShape> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> ?actKindCardinality ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#or> ?alternatives . ?actKindCardinality <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/actKind> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#nodeKind> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#IRI> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#minCount> \"1\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#maxCount> \"1\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> \"ProjectionNotification must name its authority act kind.\" . ?alternatives <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> ?evidenceFull ; <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> ?pointerlessList . ?pointerlessList <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> ?pointerless ; <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> . ?evidenceFull <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#not> ?sceneOpenedShape . ?sceneOpenedShape <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> ?sceneOpenedProperty . ?sceneOpenedProperty <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/actKind> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#hasValue> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/SceneOpened> . ?pointerless <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> ?pointerlessActKind, ?pointerlessAuthority, ?pointerlessCertificate . ?pointerlessActKind <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/actKind> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#hasValue> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/SceneOpened> . ?pointerlessAuthority <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/authorityRecord> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#maxCount> \"0\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> . ?pointerlessCertificate <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/commitCertificate> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#maxCount> \"0\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> . }",
